From 950a5394dddd9a30a7b0828fddd0019c53c88e75 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ramesh Mandal <ramesh@6epixels.com>
Date: Thu, 2 Jul 2026 13:47:26 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat(onboarding): validated identity form, avatar picker,
 profile persistence

- identity.schema.ts: zod schema (display name 2-40 chars; username 3-20,
  lowercase/numbers/underscore, leading @ stripped via transform)
- IdentityScreen: react-hook-form + zodResolver, inline errors, prefilled
  from persisted draft
- profile.store.ts: zustand persist over browser.storage.local via
  StateStorage adapter; visibility, identity, avatarColor, isComplete
- VisibilityScreen: persists public/private choice with selected state
- AvatarScreen: initials preview + 8-color radio palette, Finish completes
  profile and enters workspace
- WorkspaceScreen: placeholder proving persistence (profile header,
  visibility badge, sign out resets profile)
- App.tsx: hydration gate (no welcome flash) + returning users skip
  onboarding straight to workspace
- Avatar UI component (sm/md/lg/xl) + getInitials util
- gitignore .turbo/.output/.wxt (build artifacts were leaking into patches)
